	<pb n="0001" facs="liv_002078_0001"/><!--pb/@n='1r'-->
<lb/><p rend="no-indent"><add place="inline" rend="gray small" hand="#hand01">114 A</add><space extent="1" unit="chars"/><date when="1864-10-01">1<hi rend="sup underline">st</hi> <choice><abbr>Oct<hi rend="sup underline">r</hi></abbr><expan>October</expan></choice> 1864</date></p>
<lb/>
<!-- I have commented out the following 3 lines as they are pre-printed AM -->
<!--<lb/><p rend="right"><placeName>NEWSTEAD ABBEY,</placeName></p>
<lb/><p rend="right"><placeName>MANSFIELD</placeName></p>
<lb/><p rend="right">NOTTS.</p>-->
<lb/>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent">Dear <persName>D<hi rend="sup underline">r</hi> Tidman</persName></p>
<lb/><p><space extent="3" unit="chars"/>I called <date when="1864-09-30">yesterday</date> 
<lb/>at <placeName>Blomfield <choice><abbr>St.</abbr><expan>Street</expan></choice></placeName> &amp; 
<lb/>unfortunately missed 
<lb/>meeting you - I thank 
<lb/>you for your kind 
<lb/>note - I did not 
<lb/>answer it because 
<lb/>I was in <placeName><country>Scotland</country></placeName> &amp; 
<lb/>as I was to be only 
<lb/>one day in <placeName><settlement type="city">London</settlement></placeName>
<lb/>I thought it best 

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_002078_0002"/><!--pb/@n='1v'-->
<lb/>to save trouble by 
<lb/>waiting on you.</p>
<lb/><p>If you <choice><sic>recieve</sic><corr>receive</corr></choice> any 
<lb/>information from 
<lb/><persName>M<hi rend="sup underline">r</hi> Moffat</persName> or about 
<lb/>him I shall feel 
<lb/>much obliged by 
<lb/>your communicating 
<lb/>it at your convenience 
<lb/>as I have heard nothing 
<lb/>from him or from 
<lb/><persName>John Moffat</persName> for 
<lb/>a long time - Wishing 
<lb/>you better health &amp; 
<lb/>every blessing</p>

	<pb n="0003" facs="liv_002078_0003"/><!--pb/@n='2r'-->
<lb/><p rend="no-indent"><space extent="2" unit="chars"/>I am &amp;c</p>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent"><persName>David Livingstone</persName></p>
<lb/>
<lb/>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent"><persName>Rev<hi rend="sup underline">d</hi> D<hi rend="sup underline">r</hi> Tidman</persName></p>
			
</div>
